{
  "id": "RAW_f2fa847c",
  "title": "朝鲜黑客长期、持续攻击 npm 生态！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==&mid=2247536388&idx=1&sn=ed71fa192dd97b92c4d44dbfcb00c68b",
  "date": "2025-11-28 04:43:00",
  "author": "前端充电宝",
  "siteName": "前端充电宝",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a1dd3f3d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FEO58xpw5UMM4CaZvCzW4txkosRI9F4kaicAx2ib20n1PF5KAyVe7tMyTY7icRQpwibuLFicaz6SoDGh2l9m8oGhDG6Q%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"word-wrap:break-word;overflow:hidden;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'SF Pro Text', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\">\n    <div style=\"height: auto;\">\n     <div>\n      <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"前端充电宝\" data-alias=\"FE-Charge\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EO58xpw5UMNJLOYUj7Uv3TSiaqDldeaxxhCosR00yDKGR9lvI4y9NOfG7ADJHfKEsKuVAFWgDPqLN5afgZGkbZg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"聚焦前端开发，探索AI新浪潮：宝藏工具×前沿动态×实战技巧，解锁前端新可能！\" data-id=\"MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">相信大家都或多或少听说过朝鲜黑客盗取虚拟货币的事。但今年，他们的手伸到了我们最熟悉的地方——npm 生态。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">今年最大规模的偷币案</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">先说个今年最震撼的。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">今年 2 月 21 日深夜，加密交易所 Bybit 遭遇历史级别攻击，被盗走价值约&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">15 亿美元的以太坊</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很快，链上取证团队 ZachXBT 直接锁定幕后：还是那批熟悉的身影——</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">Lazarus（拉撒路）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这群人从 2017 年开始就没停过：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">50+ 场大型攻击</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">累计损失 37 亿美元</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">光比特币就偷了 8500+ 枚</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">他们早就把“偷币”练成了产业链。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但今年的变化是：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">他们不只偷钱，还盯上了开发者。</span></strong></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">npm：成了新的入口</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去一年，安全团队陆续揭露了几起规模惊人的 npm 污染事件：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">一次清剿直接揪出&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">338 个恶意包</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，下载量超 5 万；</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">另一批包含&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">67 个带后门包</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，累计下载 1.7 万+；</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">攻击目标包括常用工具包、前端辅助库、命令行工具、各种小型依赖。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">黑客套路非常固定：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">发布名字“差一个字母”的 typosquatting 包</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">利用 postinstall 偷偷执行脚本</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">扫文件系统、浏览器数据、SSH、npm token</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">读取环境变量、配置文件、本地缓存等敏感信息</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">收集账号密码、云服务凭证、项目密钥</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">npm 是全世界最开放的生态，这当然是优点，但也让攻击门槛低得离谱：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">发个包几十秒的事，却可能影响成千上万个项目。</span></strong></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">他们不只发恶意包，连“面试”都能下手</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">更离谱的是，攻击者已经把社工玩得炉火纯青。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">安全团队披露过一条完整的套路：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"background-color:#0066ff;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;transform:translate(0px, -1px);font-weight:bold;width:20px;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;margin-right:10px;height:20px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">伪装成海外 HR</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"background-color:#0066ff;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;transform:translate(0px, -1px);font-weight:bold;width:20px;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;margin-right:10px;height:20px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">2</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">给你发一个高薪远程机会</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"background-color:#0066ff;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;transform:translate(0px, -1px);font-weight:bold;width:20px;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;margin-right:10px;height:20px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">3</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">要你做个“技术测试”</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"background-color:#0066ff;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;transform:translate(0px, -1px);font-weight:bold;width:20px;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;margin-right:10px;height:20px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">4</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">发来一个所谓的项目模板</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"background-color:#0066ff;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;transform:translate(0px, -1px);font-weight:bold;width:20px;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;margin-right:10px;height:20px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">5</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">一运行 → 中毒</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种方式现在有了专门的名字：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">带毒面试攻击</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多开发者以为自己在做题，实际上已经把后门亲手装进了电脑。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么要盯开发者？</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">道理很简单：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">攻陷一个开发者，比攻陷一家大公司容易太多。</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且一旦得手，可能什么都能拿到：密钥、配置、环境变量、内部工具账号、部署权限……</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n        <br> \n       </span><span leaf=\"\">这比正面攻打平台省力太多了。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">前端该怎么做？</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">别觉得这事离自己很远。只要你写 Node、React、Vue、脚本、自动化流程，它都跟你有关系。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">几条能立刻提升安全性的好习惯：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">看清包名</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：typosquatting（拼错字钓鱼）太常见了。</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">注意 postinstall</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：很多恶意脚本都藏在这里。</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">开依赖审计</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">npm audit</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">pnpm audit</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;至少开一个。</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">锁版本</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：少用&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">^</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">~</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，风险小很多。</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">开发机别放生产密钥</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：环境隔离真的是基本操作。</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">对“高薪远程邀请”保持冷静</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：特别是要你跑陌生项目的。</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">延迟更新</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：pnpm 的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">minimumReleaseAge</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;给新版本加一个“冷静期”，能有效避开零小时攻击。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">写在最后</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些攻击不是偶然事件，而是系统化运作。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">偷交易所、投毒依赖、社工面试——本质上都是同一个方向：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">从开发者入口突破整个体系。</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">npm 是前端工程的入口，一旦被污染，影响的不是某个项目，而是整个行业。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们不用变成安全专家，但至少要记住一件事：</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">npm install 不是小事，它等于在给某段代码投信任票。</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">多看一眼，真的能少踩很多坑。</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章揭示朝鲜黑客组织 Lazarus 长期攻击 npm 生态，通过恶意包和社工手段窃取开发者信息，并提供了详细的防御指南。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章揭示朝鲜黑客组织 Lazarus 长期攻击 npm 生态，通过恶意包和社工手段窃取开发者信息，并提供了详细的防御指南。",
  "summary": "文章深入剖析了朝鲜黑客组织 Lazarus 对 npm 生态系统持续进行的供应链攻击和社工威胁。通过引用今年最大规模的 Bybit 加密货币盗窃案，作者指出 Lazarus 已将攻击目标从单纯的虚拟货币扩展到全球开发者。文中详细介绍了黑客常用的攻击手法，包括利用 typosquatting 发布恶意 npm 包，在 `postinstall` 脚本中植入后门，以及通过伪装成 HR 进行“带毒面试攻击”，诱骗开发者运行恶意项目以窃取敏感信息。文章强调了攻击开发者相较于直接攻击大公司的低成本和高回报，并为广大前端和 Node.js 开发者提供了多项实用且可操作的防御建议，如仔细检查包名、警惕 `postinstall` 脚本、开启依赖审计、锁定依赖版本、隔离生产密钥、警惕高薪远程面试邀请以及利用 `pnpm` 的延迟更新功能，旨在提升整个开发生态的安全防护水平。",
